    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/30/35428890/241eba6e4c00020975cf91170050f435_3516135576474445525.png",
                "id": "talent54375",
                "key": "Spear of the Church",
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Spear of the Church"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>, creates 2 stacks of <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Scope Out Soft Spots</span>. (When the Scope Out Soft Spots effect is triggered, creates <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Strike Where It Hurts</span>.)</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Scope Out Soft Spots</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Combat Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After your characters use a Skill:</span> For each stack of this effect, there is a 10% chance of creating <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Strike Where It Hurts</span>. If <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Strike Where It Hurts</span> is created, the number of stacks of this effect is halved. (Rounded down)<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Strike Where It Hurts</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Combat Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When dealing Skill DMG:</span> Remove this status and double the DMG dealt for this instance.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/30/35428890/9ec392a13f4b379cb1bf584823f2ccf6_1811351196603112031.png",
                "id": "talent22147",
                "key": "Ravaging Confession ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Ravaging Confession "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>, creates 2 stacks of <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Scope Out Soft Spots</span>, and summons <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Evercold Frostlance</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Scope Out Soft Spots</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After your characters use a Skill:</span> For each stack of this effect, there is a 10% chance of creating <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Strike Where It Hurts</span>. If <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Strike Where It Hurts</span> is created, the number of stacks of this effect is halved. (Rounded down)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/30/35428890/ae16855c8b660cd79949ed838a7d0ea4_5723528790661115461.png",
                "id": "talent36545",
                "key": "Rites of Termination",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Rites of Termination"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>, create 1 stack of <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Scope Out Soft Spots</span><br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/30/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_1491499518617027173.png",
                "id": "talent42881",
                "key": "Evercold Frostlance",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [
                  {
                    "description": "",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/30/35428890/9c8d0f6e6f09b7685da506b0948c1e47_7589197203144300929.png"
                  }
                ],
                "title": "Evercold Frostlance"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Cryo and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG+1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives Physical or Pyro DMG, in which case they will take +2 DMG)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/30/35428890/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_5334072553823336563.png",
                "id": "talent99737",
                "key": "Cryo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Cryo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/30/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_1758741847829923254.png",
                "id": "talent70184",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
